title: Counter-Strike 1.6 V28 NONSTEAM
description:
English/Englanti:

This is counter-strike 1.6 V28 Installer, install it, go to server and PLAY, It&#039;s VERY SIMPLE. Steam account/CD-Key NOT required.

You can choose Low quality (1.6 original) or High quality (which has source&#039;s weapons and models). It is recommended that you choose low quality, because it&#039;s has less lagging.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Preferences:

Release 09.03.2007 (v28)
- Newest NonSteam version
- Playable on LAN and Internet
- NonSteam MasterServer included
- Steam Account/CD-Key NOT required
- hw.dll Patch, no more Invalid CD-Key errors
- Added Original CZ bots modified for CS (the best ones available!)
- Nice installer
- Ability to choose between High Quality and Low Quality

HIGH QUALITY:
- Source player models
- Source weapon models
- Source HUD
- Realistic Blood
- Better Decals
- Better Sprites (e.g. muzzleflash)

LOW QUALITY:
- Original CS1.6 models
- Original HUD
- Original Blood, Decals, Sprites
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
